            </content><sourceNote>(<ref href="/hk/2021/er3">E.R. 3 of 2021</ref>)</sourceNote></section><section id="ID_1438402540815_003" name="s2" reason="inEffect" role="paragraph" startPeriod="2021-06-30" status="operational" temporalId="s2"><num value="2">2.</num><heading>Determination of fares</heading><content>The maximum fares that the grantee shall charge for the routes specified in the
